  "text": "Microarray design and RNA extraction DNA based arrays, produced by Agilent Technologies http://www.agilent.com, were obtained by in situ synthesis of 60 mer oligonucleotides on glass slides [CITATION_1] . For each gene, 3 to 6 different probes were randomly distributed on the array. Total RNA was extracted with the macaloïd method and purified as previously described [CITATION_2] .",
